      "content": {
        "title": "Oncologic Syndromes and Staging — Core Principles",
        "definition": "Hereditary and syndromic associations with musculoskeletal tumors including MHE, Ollier disease, and Li-Fraumeni syndrome.",
        "summary": "Multiple hereditary exostoses carry chondrosarcoma risk. Maffucci syndrome links enchondromas with hemangiomas. Recognition guides surveillance."
      },
